This pesto is fantastic. It goes with anything. Salmon is a nice choice. But I have also eaten it with shrimp and pasta, chicken, and other white fish. I even think it would be good on steak.

Rating: 2
The pesto in this recipe is delicious. A nice twist on traditional pesto. That being said, I think it would go even better with a less flavorful/fatty fish like a white fish. The salmon and pesto together was just a bit too oily and intense for our liking so while the pesto is a keeper we'll likely pair it with something else in the future. It was delicious a few days later over fried eggs and heirloom tomatoes though! Suzanne www.savorygirl.com

