Rating: 3
The pesto was so good I couldn't stop eating it. I just love anything made with pumpkin seeds. The flavor was mellow and perfectly seasoned without adding additional lime juice. I could have cooked the salmon better such as in a nonstick pan which seems to put a better crust on the skin and color on the flesh without drowning in oil or maybe I didn't use enough oil in my cast iron pan. And I think I will season the salmon a bit stronger with a touch of garlic powder and more salt too. I will make this again!

