Rating: 1
This recipe was just okay. First, the pumpkin seeds, which I roasted first, didn't have a lot of flavor so the pesto just tasted like cilantro and lime. The pistachio pesto recipe on this site is much more flavorful. Also, the salmon seemed too rich for the pesto -- perhaps because of the amount of olive oil. I have some pesto left over and I may try it on a grilled pork tenderloin tonight. I won't be making this again.